statements: SELECT * FROM Feedbacks;
SELECT feedback_id, evaluation_score FROM Feedbacks WHERE evaluation_score > 3;
SELECT volunteer_id, date_submitted FROM Feedbacks WHERE volunteer_id = 10;
SELECT feedback_text FROM Feedbacks WHERE feedback_id = 5;
SELECT * FROM Feedbacks ORDER BY date_submitted DESC;
SELECT * FROM Feedbacks WHERE evaluation_score > 3 ORDER BY date_submitted DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT feedback_id, feedback_text, evaluation_score FROM Feedbacks WHERE date_submitted > '2021-01-01' ORDER BY evaluation_score ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT volunteer_id, COUNT(*) AS feedback_count FROM Feedbacks GROUP BY volunteer_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 3 ORDER BY feedback_count DESC;
SELECT AVG(evaluation_score) AS avg_score, EXTRACT(MONTH FROM date_submitted) AS month FROM Feedbacks GROUP BY EXTRACT(MONTH FROM date_submitted) ORDER BY month ASC;
SELECT feedback_id, feedback_text FROM Feedbacks WHERE feedback_text ILIKE '%positive%' ORDER BY feedback_id ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM feedbacks WHERE satisfaction_level > 3;
SELECT id, feedback_text FROM feedbacks WHERE volunteer_id = 10;
SELECT volunteer_id, feedback_text, satisfaction_level FROM feedbacks ORDER BY satisfaction_level DESC;
SELECT * FROM feedbacks WHERE feedback_text LIKE '%improve%';
SELECT feedback_text, satisfaction_level FROM feedbacks WHERE satisfaction_level BETWEEN 2 AND 4;
SELECT id, volunteer_id, feedback_text, satisfaction_level FROM feedbacks WHERE satisfaction_level > 3
SELECT volunteer_id, feedback_text FROM feedbacks WHERE volunteer_id = 10 ORDER BY satisfaction_level DESC
SELECT * FROM feedbacks WHERE satisfaction_level BETWEEN 1 AND 3 ORDER BY id ASC
SELECT volunteer_id, feedback_text, satisfaction_level FROM feedbacks WHERE volunteer_id = 20 ORDER BY id DESC
SELECT feedback_text, satisfaction_level FROM feedbacks WHERE satisfaction_level = 5 ORDER BY feedback_text ASC
SELECT * FROM feedback;
SELECT feedback_text, feedback_date FROM feedback WHERE volunteer_id = 1;
SELECT evaluation_score, evaluation_date FROM evaluations ORDER BY evaluation_date DESC;
SELECT volunteer_name, volunteer_email FROM volunteers WHERE join_date >= '2021-01-01';
SELECT volunteer_name, active_status FROM volunteers WHERE active_status = TRUE;
SELECT volunteer_name, volunteer_email FROM volunteers;
SELECT feedback_text, feedback_date FROM feedback WHERE volunteer_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM evaluations WHERE evaluation_score > 8 ORDER BY evaluation_date DESC;
SELECT feedback_id, evaluation_score FROM feedback JOIN evaluations ON feedback.feedback_id = evaluations.feedback_id;
SELECT volunteer_name, join_date FROM volunteers WHERE active_status = TRUE ORDER BY join_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM volunteers LIMIT 10;
SELECT name, email, phone_number FROM volunteers ORDER BY name DESC;
SELECT volunteer_id, name, registration_date FROM volunteers WHERE registration_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT feedback_id, rating, feedback_date FROM feedback ORDER BY feedback_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM evaluations WHERE evaluation_score > 70 ORDER BY evaluation_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM volunteers;
SELECT name, email, phone_number FROM volunteers WHERE address IS NOT NULL ORDER BY registration_date DESC;

SELECT volunteer_id, name, email, COUNT(*) AS total_feedback FROM volunteers LEFT JOIN feedback ON volunteers.volunteer_id = feedback.volunteer_id GROUP BY volunteers.volunteer_id HAVING total_feedback > 0;

SELECT v.name, e.evaluator_id, ev.evaluation_score, ev.evaluation_notes FROM volunteers v INNER JOIN evaluations ev ON v.volunteer_id = ev.volunteer_id INNER JOIN evaluations e ON ev.evaluator_id = e.volunteer_id;
SELECT engagement_id, volunteer_id, engagement_date, engagement_type, DATEDIFF(NOW(), engagement_date) AS days_since_engagement FROM engagement WHERE duration_hours > 3 ORDER BY engagement_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM feedback;
SELECT feedback_text, rating FROM feedback WHERE rating > 3;
SELECT project_name, start_date, end_date FROM project ORDER BY start_date DESC;
SELECT volunteer.name, volunteer.email, project.project_name FROM volunteer JOIN engagement ON volunteer.id = engagement.volunteer_id JOIN project ON project.id = engagement.project_id;
SELECT evaluation_text, overall_rating FROM evaluation WHERE overall_rating < 3;
SELECT * FROM feedback;
SELECT volunteer_id, feedback_text FROM feedback WHERE rating > 4;
SELECT project_name, start_date, end_date FROM project ORDER BY start_date DESC;
SELECT volunteer.name, engagement_level, evaluation_text FROM volunteer JOIN engagement ON volunteer.id = engagement.volunteer_id JOIN evaluation ON engagement.evaluation_id = evaluation.id;
SELECT project.project_name, AVG(overall_rating) AS avg_rating FROM project JOIN evaluation ON project.id = evaluation.project_id GROUP BY project.project_name;
